title: [Icemule, Brewer's Alley]
description: The alley dead ends here at the base of an intricately carved statue set flush against the northern wall.  The cobblestones look to be in dire need of cleaning, as small bits of refuse can be seen strewn about the alley.

The alley dead ends here at the base of an intricately carved statue set flush against the northern wall.  The shadows make it difficult to see the cobblestones in any great detail, though strewn bits of refuse can be easily observed as dark unidentifiable objects here and there.
